desc_long							评测						“... easily one of 2011's best games.”95/100– GameCritics“... a triumph in almost every way possible.”10/10 – The Sixth Axis												关于这款游戏							In this Insanely Twisted, 2-D action-adventure game, explore unique environments and battle bizarre creatures as you make your way toward the center of the mysterious Shadow Planet! Solve complex puzzles and upgrade your ship with alien technology as you fight to save your home world.Key FeaturesStriking and appealing visual style by renowned artistMichel Gagné.Innovative and intuitive puzzle design mixed with intenseaction sequences.Unique and visually stunning creatures and environments.Rich worlds and captivating back stories.Explore the worlds of Insanely Twisted Shadow Planet withfriends with multiplayer.						
